クラス UniqValueCount

    UniqValueCount

    @InterfaceAudience.Public
@InterfaceStability.Stable
public class UniqValueCount
extends Object
implements ValueAggregator<Object>
    This class implements a value aggregator that dedupes a sequence of objects.
